# Pin line endings to LF in the repository.
#
# This repo is edited on Windows but the orchestrator runs on Linux (WSL2) and
# .specify/ is full of bash scripts, which break outright with CRLF. Without this,
# a checkout can flip endings and every touched file shows as wholly modified —
# 566 insertions and 566 deletions of identical content — which buries real diffs
# and makes review worthless.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Bash scripts must be LF regardless of platform or they will not execute.
*.sh text eol=lf

# Never munge binaries.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
